    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a ride that\u2019s as reliable as it is fun to drive? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s in great shape and totally ready for its next adventure! It\u2019s been well-loved and consistently maintained, making it the perfect choice for anyone who wants a solid, worry-free vehicle. It drives like a dream and still looks fantastic on the road. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you\u2019re really going to love it!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
