    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been super reliable and is still in really solid shape\u2014perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways! It\u2019s been well-loved and looked after, so you're getting a great car that's ready to hit the road right away. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
