    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine featuring individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS. This example is mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, delivering power through a variable M Differential Lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS rebuild to ensure timing precision. The suspension utilizes a refreshed multi-link rear setup and MacPherson struts up front, maintaining excellent lateral grip and turn-in response. Though it shows light aesthetic wear, the mechanical integrity is robust, with the engine pulling hard to its 7,900 RPM redline and the gearbox offering crisp, positive engagement.",
